	    </div>
	    
	    <div id="canvas-holder2" style="width:38%; float: right">		<!--Feel free to change this if I did it a stupid way. This is all I could figure out-->
	    	<h2 style="text-align:center; font-family:Arial">Income Ratio</h2>
